3: //! The controller owns no Slint handles and performs no filesystem, registry,
4: //! process, network, or desktop work. It only turns UI intents and owned worker
5: //! events into a current [`OverviewSnapshot`](crate::domain::overview::OverviewSnapshot)
6: //! so production code can keep slow work on background workers while tests can
7: //! exercise every state transition with in-memory values.
